sections.text:
To provide guidance on nutritional and technical aspects of the production of Formulated Complementary Foods for Older Infants and Young Children as defined in Section 3.1, including:
i. Formulation of such foods, based on the nutritional requirements of older infants and young children;
ii. Processing techniques;
iii. Hygienic requirements;
iv. Provisions for packaging;
v. Provisions for labelling and instructions for use.

